ent-AU14LACNclothingequipmentvendor = LACN Landing Forces apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Latin American Colonial Navy apparel for the Landing Forces. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14LACNequipmentvendor = LACN Landing Forces equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Latin American Colonial Navy equipment for the Landing Forces. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14LACNcorpsmanvendor = LACN Landing Forces corpsman medical vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of Latin American Colonial Navy trauma supplies for the Landing Forces. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14LACNaircrewvendor = LACN aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Latin American Colonial Navy aircrew flight and support gear for the Landing Forces. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14LACNcommandequipmentvendor = LACN Landing Forces command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Latin American Colonial Navy command-leadership equipment for the Landing Forces. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14LACNMGequipmentvendor = LACN Landing Forces machine gunner equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Latin American Colonial Navy light-machine gun systems for the Landing Forces. Standard issue for designated smart-gun crews on naval vessels and high-threat outposts. Built to bring fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14LACNsectionleaderequipmentvendor = LACN Landing Forces section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Latin American Colonial Navy section-leadership equipment for the Landing Forces. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14LACNWeaponsVendor = LACN Landing Forces weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Latin American Colonial Navy weaponry for the Landing Forces. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14LACNSpecialWeaponsVendor = LACN Landing Forces special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Latin American Colonial Navy heavy and breaching ordnance for the Landing Forces. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14MilitaryPolicemanVendorLACN = LACN military police equipment rack
    .desc = An automated rack hooked up to a small storage of military police equipment.
ent-AU14LACNRequisitionVendor = LACN automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
